node.text:
Cohosting with @rachelsmithtv last night on @entertainmenttonight head over to my IGTV for the full video! We talk about my hand recovery, new season of #BuddyVsDuff @foodnetwork and decorate our summer favorite @carlosbakery Americana cake 🇺🇸 
.
Repost from @rachelsmithtv
•
Move over Gigi Hadid— I think I may be the Cake Boss’ new biggest fan! 🤩 Trying my hand at cake decorating with my guest co-host Buddy Valastro. (TRYING being the key word!) Buddy, it’s a wonder I’m not STILL decorating that cake. 🐢😳😂 An update from the Cake Boss himself on his recovery after his hand was impaled in a freak accident at his home bowling alley, and he teases what’s to come on Buddy vs Duff. Thank you, Buddy, for being as sweet as your delicious cakes! ☺️🙌🏽🎂 #cakeboss #carlosbakery #sweettooth #baking
